        &lt;acceptance_criteria&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;p&gt;Como boas práticas, no ServiceNow nunca se deve atribuir uma role diretamente à um usuário. Você deve atribuir a role à um grupo, e adicionar o usuário neste grupo. Assim, ao ser adicionado no grupo, o usuário ganha todas as roles que aquele grupo tiver.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criação de Roles:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Role para usuários com permissão de leitura na aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suffix: suppliers_read&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Role for read permissions in Suppliers Apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Role para usuários com permissão de escrita na aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suffix: suppliers_write&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Role for write permissions in Suppliers Apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Role para gestores da aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Suffix: suppliers_manager&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Role for managers in Suppliers Apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10pt;"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criação de Grupos:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grupo com permissão de leitura na aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Name: Suppliers Read&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Group with read role for Suppliers Apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Roles:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.read&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Members:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Avery Parbol&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grupo com permissão de leitura na aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Name: Suppliers Write&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Group with write role for Suppliers Apps&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Roles:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.read&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.write&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Members:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Chuck Farley&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Grupo com permissão de leitura na aplicação &amp;#34;Suppliers&amp;#34;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Name: Suppliers Managers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Description: Group for Suppliers Managers&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Roles:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.read&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.write&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;x_....._suppliers.manager&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Members:
&lt;ul style="list-style-position: inside;"&gt;&lt;li&gt;Gale Nolau&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.servicenow.com/en-US/bundle/utah-platform-administration/page/administer/roles/concept/c_Roles.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://docs.servicenow.com/en-US/bundle/utah-platform-administration/page/administer/roles/concept/c_Roles.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://docs.servicenow.com/en-US/bundle/utah-platform-administration/page/administer/users-and-groups/concept/c_Groups.html" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://docs.servicenow.com/en-US/bundle/utah-platform-administration/page/administer/users-and-groups/concept/c_Groups.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;]]&gt;&lt;/acceptance_criteria&gt;
